          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊，为父倒有父子之情，难道我儿，就无有手足之义了么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹不必如此，孩儿愿去就是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，快快上马去罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹呀！"
