    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "他道我后来遭大难",
        "杨继业",
        "苏隐士"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（苏隐士上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏隐士",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "天下荒荒刀兵乱，"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏隐士",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "黎民涂炭不得安。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏隐士",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老汉，苏隐士，乃南朝人也。当年大战北国，流落在此，每日在这海上牧羊度"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏隐士",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "日。闻听南朝差来大将杨继业，被番兵杀得大败，被困在这两狼山下，内无粮"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏隐士",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "草，外无救兵，倘若被番兵擒去，可叹他一世的忠良付与流水。是老汉在苏武"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏隐士",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "庙前、李陵碑下刻下诗句一首，激他之怒，盗去宝刀，成全他一世英名也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏隐士",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "可叹忠良遭大难，"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏隐士",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "那旁来了一将官。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨继业上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "当年保驾五台山，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "智空长老对我言："
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "到如今果应那智空言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此不知什么所在？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他道我后来遭大难"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏隐士",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗯哼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那厢有一老丈，向前问来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，老丈请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏隐士",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了。这位将军，敢么失迷路途么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问老丈，此处什么所在？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏隐士",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你来看："
        },
        {
          "character": "苏隐士",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此处是两狼，前面摆战场。到此有埋伏，犯者一命亡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问老丈，在此作甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏隐士",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在此牧羊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这样兵荒马乱，你还牧的什么羊啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏隐士",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兵荒不兵荒，与我实无妨。老汉无别干，在此牧老羊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "难道这老羊还有什么贵处么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏隐士",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "提起此羊有贵处，他的名儿万古扬。生下几个羊羔子，烈烈轰轰在世上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏隐士",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前者几个死，今日一个亡。逃生是忘想，今日死老羊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "苏隐士",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老羊与我死！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "老丈说话理不通，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "分明道我杨令公！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（苏隐士收刀，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "霎时不见我的护身龙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住。老丈将我的宝刀收去。为大将者，宁舍千军，不舍寸铁。待我赶上前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“苏武庙”，进庙走走。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨继业进庙。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那厢有一碑碣，向前看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“李陵碑”，呀呀呸！汉室李陵，乃是大大的奸佞，不知何人与他立的什么碑"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "碣！上面还有几行小字，待我仔细看来："
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "庙是苏武庙，碑是李陵碑，令公来到此，卸甲又丢盔！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨继业丢盔弃甲。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住！老夫被困在两狼山，盼兵兵不到，望子子不归，白日受饥饿，夜晚被风"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吹。也罢，不免拜谢宋王爵禄之恩，我就碰死在李陵碑下！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨继业碰碑，死。）"
        }
      ],
